Vance Crawford"The Vice"Ht: 5'9" WT: 155lbs Season W/L record ( 0-0)Cameron Kincade"The Kin-Killer-Cade"Ht: 5'10" WT: 155lbsSeason W/L record (0-0)
Here for the very first time on Naked Kombat are combatants Vance "The Vice" Crawford taking on Cameron "The Kin-Killer-Cade". Cameron has martial arts training in MMA as well as Jiu Jitsu and he doesn't think Vance's wrestling background will be any trouble at all. Vance attacks Cameron quickly bringing him to the ground and manages to sit on his face, smothering him as he punches Cameron's gut. For the first time of the season, both studs are oiled up for the last wrestling round when Vance gets caught in a strong full nelson. Their glistening muscled bodies slide and flip around the mat as they fight balls to the wall for sexual domination, but only one can come out on top, while the other gets humiliated and fucked into submission.
title: Cameron "The Kin-Killer-Cade" vs Vance "The Vice" Crawford - Oil Match
